  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.88,
      "text": "Second, the prompt, your specification of what you want."
    },
    {
      "start": 3.08,
      "end": 4.64,
      "text": "The prompt doesn't define the walls."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.14,
      "end": 6.12,
      "text": "Tests do that."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.66,
      "end": 9.34,
      "text": "The prompt defines what you're asking for and why."
    },
    {
      "start": 11.46,
      "end": 12.76,
      "text": "And here's something subtle."
    },
    {
      "start": 13.6,
      "end": 16.1,
      "text": "The exact implementation can vary."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.86,
      "end": 18.3,
      "text": "What's locked is the behavior."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.16,
      "end": 20.24,
      "text": "The code is flexible."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.88,
      "end": 22.08,
      "text": "The contract is fixed."
    },
    {
      "start": 22.98,
      "end": 25.94,
      "text": "A good prompt is much smaller than the code it generates."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.94,
      "end": 29.2,
      "text": "You're specifying what and why, not how."
    },
    {
      "start": 30.84,
      "end": 32.02,
      "text": "Third, grounding."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.62,
      "end": 35.52,
      "text": "This determines the properties of what fills the mold."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.78,
      "end": 39.16,
      "text": "Grounding is learned from your past generations."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.8,
      "end": 42.28,
      "text": "When you successfully generate and fix code,"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.72,
      "end": 44.64,
      "text": "that knowledge feeds back into the system."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.66,
      "end": 48.84,
      "text": "Your style, your patterns, your team's conventions."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.62,
      "end": 51.12,
      "text": "Grounding captures all of it"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.12,
      "end": 54.16,
      "text": "and applies it automatically to future generations."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.94,
      "end": 60.48,
      "text": "Prompt plus tests plus grounding, intent plus constraints plus style."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.92,
      "end": 63.46,
      "text": "Together, they form a complete specification."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.7,
      "end": 66.18,
      "text": "The code is output."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.74,
      "end": 67.68,
      "text": "The mold is what matters."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.3,
      "end": 73.52,
      "text": "Now, here's something subtle that changes how you think about prompts."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.76,
      "end": 77.06,
      "text": "In 3D printing, there's no mold."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.6,
      "end": 81.5,
      "text": "The machine must know exactly where to place every single point of material."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.5,
      "end": 84.7,
      "text": "The specification must be extremely precise."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.46,
      "end": 88.94,
      "text": "In injection molding, precision comes from the walls."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.52,
      "end": 91.8,
      "text": "The material just flows until it's constrained."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.82,
      "end": 96.36,
      "text": "This maps directly to PDD."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.98,
      "end": 101.7,
      "text": "With few tests, your prompt needs to specify everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.48,
      "end": 107.48,
      "text": "Edge cases, error handling, exact behavior in every situation."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.48,
      "end": 112.34,
      "text": "With many tests, the prompt only needs to specify intent."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.96,
      "end": 114.54,
      "text": "The tests handle the constraints."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.22,
      "end": 119.2,
      "text": "This is why test accumulation matters."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.9,
      "end": 121.58,
      "text": "It's not just about catching bugs."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.36,
      "end": 126.56,
      "text": "It's about making prompts simpler and regeneration safer over time."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.7,
      "end": 131.72,
      "text": "More tests, less prompt, the walls do the precision work."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.88,
      "end": 136.2,
      "text": "Hmm, let's talk about compound returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.48,
      "end": 141.02,
      "text": "When you patch code, each fix has local returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.48,
      "end": 143.26,
      "text": "You fixed one bug in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.78,
      "end": 146.0,
      "text": "Similar bugs can still occur elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.62,
      "end": 149.08,
      "text": "And sometimes your patch introduces new bugs."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.12,
      "end": 152.14,
      "text": "The returns are linear at best."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.86,
      "end": 153.96,
      "text": "Often sub-linear."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.58,
      "end": 159.62,
      "text": "When you add a test in PDD, the returns are different."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.18,
      "end": 164.24,
      "text": "That test you wrote today, it constrains tomorrow's generation."
    },
    {
      "start": 164.24,
      "end": 167.6,
      "text": "And next weeks, and next years, it's a permanent wall."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.62,
      "end": 171.58,
      "text": "Every investment in the mold has compound returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.02,
      "end": 174.74,
      "text": "Every investment in patching has diminishing returns."
    }
  ]
}